# KIOMS Privacy Policy

Effective Date: August 2, 2025

KIOMS respects and protects the privacy of its users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use the KIOMS app.

## 1. Data Collection
KIOMS does not collect any personal information without your permission. The app may collect:

- Device type and OS version (for performance)
- Voice input or text (for AI response purposes)
- Optional emotional responses (if enabled)
- Premium features (if subscribed)

KIOMS never collects passwords, ID card numbers, or financial data.

## 2. Premium & AI Memory
When you activate Premium Mode, your preferences and selected chat memories may be stored securely on our server to improve your experience. You can clear your memory at any time in the settings.

## 3. Local Data & Offline Mode
KIOMS allows users to use AI offline with a downloaded brain. All data used in offline mode remains on your device and is never sent to any server.

## 4. Data Security
All collected data is encrypted and protected against unauthorized access. We use industry-standard security practices.

## 5. Children's Privacy
KIOMS includes a Kid Mode to protect young users. No sensitive data is collected in Kid Mode. The app complies with international child safety laws.

## 6. Data Deletion
You can delete all your data at any time by:
- Clearing your chat memory
- Deleting the app
- Requesting data removal via email

## 7. Third-Party Services
KIOMS may use AI APIs (e.g., OpenAI) and secure payment systems like Google Play Billing. These services have their own privacy policies.

## 8. Contact
If you have any questions about this policy or want to request data removal, contact:

